            "title": "Fruit–frugivore dependencies are important in Ebolavirus outbreaks in Sub‐Saharan Africa",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Mekala",
                    "lastName": "Sundaram"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
