            "title": "Detection of Dengue Virus in Bat Flies (Diptera: Streblidae) of Common Vampire Bats, Desmodus rotundus, in Progreso, Hidalgo, Mexico",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Judith",
